  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the effectiveness of two airway clearance
      techniques; Intrapulmonary Percussive Ventilation and Assisted Autogenic Drainage in
      hospitalized infants under the age of 2 with acute viral bronchiolitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
